text: Pound Puppies is a Canadian-American computer-animated television series that launched on 10th October 2010 and created by David Sacks. == Voice artists == * Eric McCormack as Lucky and Ace * Yvette Nicole Brown as Cookie and Fluffy * John DiMaggio as Niblet and Tiny * Alanna Ubach as Strudel and Kugel * Michael Rapaport as Squirt and Squeak * Brooke Goldner as Rebound * Cree Summer as Cupcake * Jessica DiCicco as Patches == Other websites == * * Category:Canadian children's television series Category:American children's television series Category:2010s American animated television series Category:2010 Canadian television series debuts Category:Canadian animated television series Category:English-language television programs
